Package fr.B4D.socket

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DofusSocket
    The DofusSocket class represent a dofus socket.
    DofusSocketHelper
    The DofusSocketHelper class is used to find values within a socket.
    DofusSocketIterator
    The DofusSocketIterator class is used to iterate through a socket to extract values.
    PcapsFinder
    Function provider for pcap network interface.
    SocketElement
    The SocketElement class represent an element in a socket.
    SocketListener
    La classe SocketListener permet d'écouter de sniffer et traiter les trames dofus.

    Cette classe étend la classe Thread.
    SocketUtils
    The SocketUtils class is used to define useful methods relative to sockets.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SocketType
    The class SocketType defines all the known sockets and map it with the corresponding socket parser.
